CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - This Charming Quartet includes Mrs. James Lewis, wife of the new Frog President, who chats with three fashionable feminine guests; Mrs. Kenneth Mason, Miss Beverly Frazier and Mrs. Norman Johnson. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. James Lewis, Mrs. Kenneth Mason, Beverly Frazier, and Mrs. Norman Johnson, posed in front of Christmas tree, in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
